{"comments":"WetMedia Dynamics — Physics integration for tilt-responsive paint.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nThis module bridges wet media simulation with the Physics pillar.\nWhen you tilt your phone, stacked paint should slide according to:\n\n  flowVelocity = wetness × (1 - viscosity) × gravityComponent\n\n## Coordinate System\n\nDevice tilt maps to gravity direction:\n  - TiltX (roll): Left/right tilt (-90 to +90 degrees)\n  - TiltY (pitch): Forward/back tilt (-90 to +90 degrees)\n  - Combined with device gravity to get flow direction\n\n## Dependencies\n- Prelude\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Brush.WetMedia.Atoms\n- Math (sin, cos)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Gravity direction derived from device tilt.\n\nRepresents the direction \"down\" points in canvas space.\nNormalized 2D vector (x, y) where magnitude indicates tilt severity.\n  - (0, 0) = device flat, no flow\n  - (-1, 0) = tilted left, paint flows left\n  - (0, 1) = tilted forward, paint flows down (toward user)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["x",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["y",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[109,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[106,1]},"title":"GravityDirection"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert device tilt angles to gravity direction.\n\ntiltX: Roll angle in degrees (-90 to +90)\n  - Negative = tilted left\n  - Positive = tilted right\n\ntiltY: Pitch angle in degrees (-90 to +90)\n  - Negative = tilted back (away from user)\n  - Positive = tilted forward (toward user)\n\nReturns normalized gravity direction in canvas space.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","WetMedia","Dynamics"],"GravityDirection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[122,54],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[122,1]},"title":"tiltToGravity"},{"children":[],"comments":"Device flat (no tilt)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","WetMedia","Dynamics"],"GravityDirection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[147,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[147,1]},"title":"gravityFlat"},{"children":[],"comments":"Tilted left (45 degrees)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","WetMedia","Dynamics"],"GravityDirection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[151,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[151,1]},"title":"gravityTiltedLeft"},{"children":[],"comments":"Tilted right (45 degrees)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","WetMedia","Dynamics"],"GravityDirection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[155,39],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[155,1]},"title":"gravityTiltedRight"},{"children":[],"comments":"Tilted forward (45 degrees)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","WetMedia","Dynamics"],"GravityDirection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[159,41],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[159,1]},"title":"gravityTiltedForward"},{"children":[],"comments":"Tilted back (45 degrees)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","WetMedia","Dynamics"],"GravityDirection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[163,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[163,1]},"title":"gravityTiltedBack"},{"children":[],"comments":"Velocity of paint flow in canvas space.\n\nUnits: pixels per second (normalized to canvas scale)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["vx",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["vy",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[177,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brush/WetMedia/Dynamics.purs","start":[174,1]},"title":"FlowVelocity"},{"children":[],"comments":"Calculate paint flow velocity based on physical parameters.\n\nFlow velocity = wetness × (1 - viscosity) × gravity × scale\n\nParameters:\n  - wetness: How wet the paint is (0-100%)\n  - viscosity: Resistance to flow (0-100%)\n  - gravity: Direction and magnitude of tilt\n  - scale: Pixels per unit gravity (default 100)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brush","WetMedia","Atoms"],"Wetn